# Untitled UI Components

- Always use Untitled UI components exactly as generated by the Untitled UI CLI.
- Do not build approximations, wrappers, or replacement implementations for Untitled UI components unless the user explicitly confirms that custom code is needed.
- If an Untitled UI component file is missing, add the official component set with the Untitled UI CLI or ask the user before writing a local version.
- When the user provides an Untitled UI snippet, treat that snippet as the source of truth for imports, props, and composition.
- If the component cannot be installed or generated, stop and report the blocker instead of recreating it from scratch.
